      <title>劳埃德银行计划将 SRT 与 10 亿英镑英国重组抵押贷款挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/lloyds-plans-srt-tied-to-1-billion-of-uk-restructured-mortgages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，劳埃德银行集团有限公司正在出售与约 10 亿英镑（13 亿美元）英国抵押贷款相关的重大风险转移，这些抵押贷款已受到期限延长等修改的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/lloyds-plans-srt-tied-to-1-billion-of-uk-restructured-mortgages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 13:28:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>生物科技亿万富翁黄颂雄因 ImmunityBio 股票变动被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/biotech-billionaire-soon-shiong-sued-over-immunitybio-stock-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生物科技亿万富翁黄松雄 (Patrick Soon-Shiong) 在一场股东诉讼中被指控误导 ImmunityBio Inc. 的投资者了解该公司旗舰抗癌药物的前景，以此来损害投资者的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/biotech-billionaire-soon-shiong-sued-over-immunitybio-stock-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 13:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
